descriptionHtml:
So yes, i broke my word, and made a Object anyway, only because i found out that my Father doesnt do anything with easter :P

i hope you guys enjoy it.

PS. do you guys think i should spend more time / detail to my meshes? or should i keep them like i do now? i\'m still open for hints, tips  and suggestions.
